  "texts": [
    "Question templates were then combined with the entity to create the definition question.",
    "Negative questions are created by using entities from previous dialogue turns.",
    "Replacements.",
    "For each step of the plan, a replaceable element is selected and the user request is then simulated using a set of templates.",
    "In practice, we randomly select an ingredient from the intersection of the step ingredients, a database of ingredient substitutions and a list of all ingredients that occur 4 or fewer times across all recipes."
